    ("LOC_GAME_CITY_STATES_START_WITH_WALLS",               "Free Walls for City-States"),
    ("LOC_GAME_CITY_STATES_START_WITH_WALLS_DESCRIPTION",   "City-States will start with Walls in their city."),
